  <problem xml:id="prob_RatioTest">
    <title>The Ratio Test</title>
    <idx><h>sequences</h><h>Ratio Test for</h></idx>

    <introduction>
      <p>
        Suppose <m>\left(s_n\right)</m> is a sequence of positive numbers such that
        <me>
          \limit{n}{\infty}{\left(\frac{s_{n+1}}{s_n}\right)}=L
